         i didnt see this method mentioned so i'll do it:</P><P>i used this method to break the sentient armor (3 spawn) camp long ago when i twinked out my SK with the stuff...</P><P>the trick to this is a combination of pathing and having alot of room to move around... i would fear the one i wanted to kill... the other ones would commence to chase me... i would then run away, and FD. once the other two walked away i would stand up (by this point the feared one is still feared) i then follow them towards the spawn. the fear should be about to wear off by this point. id wait near the spawn and when it appeared i would then bring it to my pet. let my pet tank it for a bit while i darkness then id refear/DOT as needed. this worked great for sentient armor. although ive also used the darkness/FD trick to do the same thing it tends to be more difficult with the sentient armor because of the large assist radius.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

