        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I can think of a few suggestions not mentioned so far.<BR>I use this one to break up the protector of zek in the kael arena and you can use a variation. 3 mobs close together, I blind one(bioluminscent orb) and feign, 2 reset 3rd is still running away, i get up and tag him. you can fear the one and let others reset if you like. </P><P>ST was suggested, or you could root one, then another.</P><P>Here's a novel approach too. Charm 1 and let him fight the other 2 until he's dead, feign. get up charm other until one dies, feign. now you have a single weak mob, and a broken camp.</P><P>Thana</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
